title: Hellboy
description: Near the end of the 2nd World War, the Nazis attempt to eliminate your enemies using black magic. One of the experiments is an attempt to invoke occult forces. One such ritual is interrupted by the Allied forces, which are a boy-looking demon and his right hand made ??of stone, despite the ritual has not been completed. The boy happens to be called Hellboy and is taken by the Allies. Sixty years later, Hellboy fights for good and now is called when a strange phenomenon, possibly supernatural happens.
